{
  "texts": [
    "Importantly, this model is trivially extensible with new matching algorithms and new imaging modalities.All data served by NeuronBridge is available for programmatic access via open data APIs (Open Data API) allowing for reuse and integration.",
    "These APIs have already enabled the creation of several third-party applications including the Neuronbridger R API (http:// natve rse.",
    "org/ neuro nbrid ger) and FlyBrainLab NeuroNLP [50].",
    "The serverless back-end automatically scales to meet additional load from these API users and imposes rate limits to avoid impacts on overall service performance.",
    "Results and discussionNeuronBridge currently serves over 500 million precomputed matches between 6773 driver lines and 54,061 EM neuron skeletons."
  ]
}